# title: The Rhythmic Jazz of the 80's
# date:  2010-04-27 01:36:23
# tags:  mix, 80s, jazz, my, jazz-rock

[img/rhythmicjazz-cover.jpg]

Recently I took jazz loyalty pills in and now gonna present you my compilation of the rhythmic side of the soviet jazz. There were many abstract themes recorded that time, but just a little of ones strongly based on the rhythm. Here go some of such ones: partially jazz-rock & jazz-funk. The participants are: “Medeo”, “Boomerang”, Igor Nazaruk, “Arsenal”, “Allegro”, Konstantin Petrosyan, Tatevik Oganesyan.

[other/rhythmicjazz-preview.mp3] 

http://rapidshare.com/files/380713032/rhythmic-jazz.zip
http://narod.ru/disk/20170035000/rhythmic-jazz.zip.html
1 hr, 84 MB, mixed

Медео — Сад ветров (1982 live)
Бумеранг — Индия (1985)
Игорь Назарук — Танцуй, коляда! (1982)
Арсенал — Рэгтайм (1981)
Аллегро — Концертная сюита в трёх частях (1985)
Аллегро — В этом мире (1982)
Аллегро — Композиция на тему К.Портера (1985)
Константин Петросян — Концерт для голоса и оркестра (1987)
